49:05.548 --> 49:06.924
Why should he?

49:07.300 --> 49:08.870
A simple reason, McCoy.

49:08.975 --> 49:10.593
Let's get down to it.

49:10.804 --> 49:13.091
Radio's rapping about $750,000.

49:13.847 --> 49:15.887
There's a half a million, here.

49:17.935 --> 49:20.093
A little more was taken out before.

49:20.854 --> 49:23.689
You see, my brother's
the director of that bank.

49:23.941 --> 49:26.479
We had a few problems we had to iron out.

49:29.530 --> 49:31.487
Okay. We covered you...

49:33.158 --> 49:34.158
Yeah.

49:34.451 --> 49:36.029
You surely did, Doc.

49:43.335 --> 49:46.122
